CBRE is delighted to present, 3/46-50 Sheehan Road, Heidelberg West, for lease.

This newly refurbished 1,200sqm* building previously used as a gym, is ready to be turned back into a modern warehouse/showroom solution for your business. The building has recently been re-wired, painted and extended amenities including showers installed.

With immediate access onto Bell Street and Waterdale Road, properties of this size rarely become available in this location.

Property features include;
+ Total building size: 1,200sqm*
+ Warehouse size: 900sqm*
+ Office/showroom size: 300sqm*
+ Seventeen (17) car spaces
+ Two (2) container height roller doors
+ Three (3) phase power
+ Five (5) showers 
+ Great amenities
+ High clearance warehouse
+ Clear span
+ 10km* from Melbourne's CBD
+ Available now!

For further information or to arrange an on-site inspection, please contact the CBRE team.

*approximate

CBRE is pleased to present Unit 1/661 Waterdale Road, Heidelberg West for lease, available now.

This 1,162sqm* office/showroom/warehouse has prime corner positioning with massive 10 metre clearance in the clear span warehouse. 

Located 12km* from Melbourne's CBD, just off Bell Street with direct linkage to all major arterials, the property features the following:

+ Total building area: 1,162sqm*
+ Office area: 182sqm*
+ Warehouse area: 980sqm*
+ 10m internal clearance
+ Fourteen (14) on-site car parks
+ Great natural light
+ Three (3) phase power
+ Modern open plan office
+ Close to CBD

*approx.

- Total building area: 1,162sqm*
- Fully fitted corporate office: 182sqm*
- Twelve (12) metre high clearance, clear span warehouse: 980sqm*
- Container height roller shutter door
- Three (3) phase power
- Ample onsite parking
- Excellent inner northern location with great access to public transport, La Trobe University, Metropolitan Ring Road & Bell Street

*approx.

CBRE is pleased to present 26 Dougharty Road, Heidelberg West, for lease.

The property is highly exposed on the corner of Dougharty and Bamfield Roads, providing exceptional access to major arterials such as Lower Plenty Road and Waiora Road.

Features include:
+ Building area: 4,465sqm*
+ Warehouse area: 3,640sqm*
+ Two-level corporate office: 825sqm*
+ Five (5) on-grade roller shutter doors
+ Exceptional rear loading area
+ Ample on-site car parking
+ Three (3) phase power

For further information regarding this opportunity or to arrange an inspection of the site, kindly contact CBRE.

*approx.
